Content: My name is Jeff. I have been riding for going on 50 years now. Grew up in the Great State of Texas. Moved to Colorado when it was still a nice place to live. Currently in North Central West Virginia. I am a recovering Harley Davidson owner. My current ride is a 2019 Indian Roadmaster. Glad to be here.
